{"tid":1636011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術] 制高+放哨","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T17:23:35.000Z","uid":164378,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6940322860f9b40eea6898e90bedfa04b4cb491b","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"跪求大家聽我指指點點兩句再spread開去，歡迎理性討論，希望手足可以愈做愈好。<br />\n<br />\n首先我發夢時發現2大問題，而呢2個問題係需要全手足既意識黎填補。<br />\n<br />\n第一個係戰術報陣，大家成日前都聽到d狗係邊度&quot;佈防&quot;，其實同樣地我地都係需要佈防。目的唔同既係，我地佈防唔係要死守，而係要保護主群既手足令佢地可以安心發夢、爭取時間同確保逃生路線。最簡單就係制高，每有天橋/商場/建築物既地方就會出現制高點，而我地需要做既就係去搶先佔據(霸)左佢。我地唔需要死守制高，但係一定唔可以留空任由d狗去係高處射死我地既手足。eg. 灣仔軒尼詩道好多天橋，好多時發夢都無手足係上面或者得d街坊同和理飛，搞到好易無左優勢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上水魔法既發展/進化，制高點既重要性係唔可以忽略。<br />\n<br />\n其實唔同地形仲有好多唔同需要搶佔既地方，不過太多種類，希望可以拋磚引玉，等高人指點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2係放哨，發夢時放哨同telegram係好唔同，因為手足基本上係無咩時間睇電話，同埋telegram 資訊太散亂。現場係好需要手足周圍放哨，主要係需要留意小街內街、狗鐵出口等。目的係唔可以比狗包圍或者埋伏。現場放哨同時需要留意狗動向，最好係配合live map同現場跑動去追蹤同預計狗既位置方向，咁我地手足就可以防範於未然，更甚作出策略反包圍狗/埋伏。記住我地人數係多過佢，呢d工作唔一定係勇手足都做到，和理非既功能唔止咁少。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家要發夢發得聰明，用腦去發，想盡一切方法去保護手足，唔只係不被捕不受傷，仲要戰勝對手。<br />\n<br />\n祝各位 出入平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdee9c852e2c7d4159b2b802ffa95138481b633","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6425f760b88407620bcbb5152e94d0109ab5617f","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"自推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0ea66c31a3c2f78226164b598f26d60a037491","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"自推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb634127971a806fe97ef0f7644e3b8c103d1a91","tid":1636011,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"10月4日冇咩事唔係因為快閃成功<br />\n而係林奠又製造多一次721, 無警時分<br />\n<br />\n前線要再進化, 唔好18區約同一時間<br />\n唔好以為同時進行, 狗會唔夠人<br />\n幾多老解冇人知<br />\n<br />\ntg俾狗滲透晒<br />\n自己朋友, 同學, 同事, 10個左右一組<br />\n確保冇鬼<br />\n隨時裝修<br />\n一定要blackbloc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家暫時只係裝修黨鐵 (其他裝飾, 打掃)<br />\nTwitter RichScotford: 黨鐵重回正軌四大條件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624558</a><br />\n文宣要幫手宣傳"},{"pid":"ecd77449b72b02f1c1c3b765ef3fd26805041a27","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"自推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312bc80b45f146017ff70e1db0b38da67eab86de","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"自推5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22ce522571cc76fc77c282e1aa08e3681bc9424","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"自推6<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026da141ac797f05296ff5f868045ec3ebf6354f","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"自推7<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ea8b25531b78a16c25da7b43c5665b0254d88a","tid":1636011,"uid":299164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71535768_1424727811026002_1186793631042764800_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_oc=AQkId2I-xyK0ItxdDsrmE3f5NnB7jbEGgLpuG98esW1Neqsfsj40J3GhzjHl56-v7Q4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=5d22ec0c633f497119305890d50a15fd&amp;oe=5E1EB6AC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71535768_1424727811026002_1186793631042764800_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_oc%3DAQkId2I-xyK0ItxdDsrmE3f5NnB7jbEGgLpuG98esW1Neqsfsj40J3GhzjHl56-v7Q4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D5d22ec0c633f497119305890d50a15fd%26oe%3D5E1EB6AC&h=f9f10f2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de5c780ef85331383872973e8864cc36f3c23af9","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"自推8<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843852df3f3883cf43691d5c431194f6bf45cf48","tid":1636011,"uid":69761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"人夠多打完狗先立即跑,唔阻佢地,一定拉幾件"},{"pid":"d4111723cb29a861452638ffef8bf7ed54cd183d","tid":1636011,"uid":146837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"深水埗手足有無發現 防暴唔敢入長沙灣道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6a7b18ebd703309aef113b7fc012dc91aa3e32","tid":1636011,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"自推9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8ecc0840724dee9030c76a657c280e3970aaf7","tid":1636011,"uid":89873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face